*wcslib-4.5.3 (23 Sep 2010)

  23 Sep 2010; Sébastien Fabbro <bicatali@gentoo.org>
  files/wcslib-4.4.4-destdir.patch, +wcslib-4.5.3.ebuild,
  +files/wcslib-4.5.3-fortran.patch, metadata.xml:
  Version bump. Ebuild now allows to disable cfitsio, fortran and pgplot
  dependencies.

*wcslib-4.5 (21 Jul 2010)

  21 Jul 2010; Sébastien Fabbro <bicatali@gentoo.org> -wcslib-4.4.3.ebuild,
  -wcslib-4.4.4.ebuild, +wcslib-4.5.ebuild:
  Version bump

*wcslib-4.4.4-r1 (22 May 2010)

